com.chrismin13.additionsapi.permissions

Class ItemPermissions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chrismin13.additionsapi.permissions.ItemPermissions
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArmorPermissions, BowPermissions, CarrotStickPermissions, ElytraPermissions, FishingRodPermissions, FlintAndSteelPermissions, HoePermissions, ShearPermissions, ShieldPermissions, SpadePermissions

    public class ItemPermissions
extends Object
    This specifies the permissions that will be checked when using the Custom Item. There are similar classes available for most other types of Custom Items.
    Author:
    chrismin13

    • Constructor Detail

      • ItemPermissions

        public ItemPermissions(String permissionPrefix,
                       PermissionType type)
        Create a new ItemPermissions Object
        Parameters:
        permissionPrefix - The first part of the permission node - must be simmilar to "plugin_name.item_name". By default, this is taken from the Custom Item's Id Name.
        type - The PermissionType of the permission node. Will go right after the permissionPrefix
